==English==
[[Image:Earth-worm_1.jpg|thumb|right|250px|an earthworm]]
===Etymology===
[[earth]] + [[worm]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# A [[worm]] that lives in the [[ground]]; a worm of [[Lumbricidae]] family, or, more generally, of [[Lumbricina]] suborder.
# A disparaging reference to a [[person]], particularly one who [[grovel]]s.
# A figurative reference to [[death]].

